Package: quickSentiment
Title: A Fast and Flexible Pipeline for Text Classification
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alabhya", "Dahal", email = "alabhya.dahal@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a complete and modular pipeline for text classification. 
    Includes functions for text preprocessing, multiple vectorization methods 
    (Bag-of-Words, TF-IDF), and a suite of high-performance machine learning models 
    (e.g., glmnet, ranger, xgboost). Designed to be easily extensible for 
    comparing different modeling approaches.
